high_descs: Turn around and walk across the kitchen towards the stove, then turn right and go to the counter top above the dishwasher.
Pick up the butter knife near the edge of the counter, above the dishwasher.
Turn around and walk to the stove to your right.
Put the knife in the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan from the stove, with the knife inside it.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn left just before the door and go to the table in the corner.
Place the pan with the knife inside, on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a knife on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the counter to the left of the toaster.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and veer right to the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot.
Turn around and veer left to the round black table in the corner.
Place the pot on the table next to the wall.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn to your left walk forward then turn right head to the counter top beside the toaster
Pick up the knife on the counter top beside the toaster
Turn to your left then walk forward turn right on the stove
Put the knife in the pot on the stove
Pick up the pot with knife
Turn to your right walk forward then turn left facing the table
Put the pot with knife on the far right of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with knife on the table
